          h2 Quill revolutionizes how people learn the grammar of language.
          p Students currently learn grammatical rules by writing out sentences by hand. This system is ineffective because it results in mounds of papers for teachers to grade. Each language has a myriad of rules, which means that teaching grammar is a time intensive process.
          p Since proper grammar is essentially proper syntax, we can automate the process of grading these lessons. This gives teachers more time to work on more important problems and it ensures that students receive as much feedback as they need to master grammatical concepts.

